# This example is fully self-contained and needs no API keys.
#
# It uses a deterministic in-process model (DemoLlm) and a self-contained
# CodeRuntime (LineScriptRuntime). To adapt it for a real provider, add the
# relevant key here (e.g. GEMINI_API_KEY=...) and swap DemoLlm for an
# adk-model provider in src/main.rs.

# Optional: tune log verbosity (e.g. info, debug).
# RUST_LOG=warn
